      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition and represents the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the body is entirely free of any chips, dings, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' state, with premium upholstery that shows no signs of wear and all technological features functioning perfectly. Meticulously maintained with a full service history, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory, offering a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a truly mint-condition example.",
