    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car, so it's in total pristine condition without a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel that's so hard to find. I'm looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Drop me a message and come take a look\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
